          <p>A Grithosian does not cower before this. You do not doom-scroll through collapse fantasies. You do not retreat to a simpler time that no longer exists. You walk forward. You learn what is being built. You understand who benefits and who bears the cost. And you keep your eyes open — because the person walking forward with clear vision will always outperform the one standing still with clenched fists.</p>
